title: Red Fang Discography
description:
2009 - Red Fang
2011 - Murder the Mountains
2013 - Whales and Leeches

These were found elsewhere as single FLAC files paired with CUE files.  
I split them into tracks using CUETools.
Properly repackaged, renamed, re-tagged, and sorted.

Sounds quality is excellent on all albums.  I hear a little crackling during parts of a few songs on the self-titled album.  That's about it.

If you enjoy, please buy their merch and go to a show.
